      "instruction": "<p>Boil a full kettle</p><p>Peel and slice your <strong>shallot[s]</strong> finely</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p>",
