    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced shallot</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 2-3 min, or until softened</p>",
