      "instruction": "<p>Once softened, add the <strong>halved cherry tomatoes</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until starting to soften</p><p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong>, <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>sugar</strong> in 50ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[65ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[85ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your <strong>balsamic stock</strong></p>",
