      "instruction": "<p>Once the tomatoes have softened, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and <strong>tomato paste</strong> to the pan and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong>, <strong>balsamic stock</strong>, <strong>dried basil</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>pepper</strong> to the pan</p><p>Stir it all together and cook for 3-4 min or until thickened</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1675778070989-x200.jpg",
