    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the gnocchi is cooking, wash your <strong>spinach</strong> then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Once the tomato sauce has thickened, add the <strong>spinach</strong> to the pan and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Cook for 1-2 min or until the spinach has just wilted – this is your <strong>cherry</strong> <strong>tomato & spinach sauce</strong></p>",
