    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>cooked gnocchi</strong> to the <strong>cherry tomato & spinach sauce</strong> with a small splash of the <strong>starchy cooking water</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and cook for 1-2 min or until the sauce is thick and rich – this is your <strong>plant-based cherry tomato & spinach gnocchi</strong></p>",
